209:Last-tick instrumentation returned by `world.getMetrics()`. In `instrumentationProfile: 'minimal'`, implicit `step()` refreshes only the coarse metrics fields. In `instrumentationProfile: 'release'`, implicit `step()` leaves this as `null`; explicit `stepWithResult()` still refreshes the full metrics payload.
