1371:
1372:```typescript
1373:registerSystem(
1374:  system:
1375:    | System<TEventMap, TCommandMap>
1376:    | SystemRegistration<TEventMap, TCommandMap>
1377:    | LooseSystem
1378:    | LooseSystemRegistration,
