3109:## Path Service
3110:
3111:Grid-first path utilities and deterministic request processing built on top of the generic `findPath()` implementation.
3112:
3113:```typescript
3114:import {
3115:  PathCache,
3116:  PathRequestQueue,
3117:  createGridPathCacheKey,
3118:  createGridPathQueue,
3119:  findGridPath,
3120:  gridPathPassabilityVersion,
3121:  type GridPathConfig,
3122:  type GridPathRequest,
3123:  type PathRequestQueueEntry,
3124:  type PathRequestQueueOptions,
3125:  type PathRequestQueueStats,
3126:} from 'civ-engine';
3127:```
3128:
3129:### `findGridPath(config)`
3130:
3131:```typescript
3132:findGridPath(config: GridPathConfig): PathResult<Position> | null
3133:```
3134:
3135:Finds a path on a 2D grid using integer `Position` coordinates.
3136:
3137:**Behavior details:**
3138:- Requires either `width` and `height`, or an `occupancy` grid
3139:- Treats blocked occupancy cells as impassable
3140:- Uses orthogonal movement by default
3141:- Uses diagonal movement with octile heuristic when `allowDiagonal` is `true`
3142:- Prevents diagonal corner cutting by default
3143:- Returns positions instead of flat cell indices
3144:
3145:```typescript
3146:const result = findGridPath({
3147:  occupancy,
3148:  movingEntity: unitId,
3149:  start: { x: 12, y: 8 },
3150:  goal: { x: 40, y: 25 },
3151:  allowDiagonal: false,
3152:});
3153:```
3154:
