4464:## World History Recorder
4465:
4466:Short-horizon recorder for recent command outcomes and tick traces. Useful for AI agents, tests, and debug tooling that need recent history without building a full replay system.
4467:
4468:```typescript
4469:import {
4470:  WorldHistoryRecorder,
4471:  summarizeWorldHistoryRange,
4472:  type WorldHistoryRangeSummary,
4473:  type WorldHistoryState,
4474:  type WorldHistoryTick,
4475:} from 'civ-engine';
4476:```
4477:
4478:### Constructor
4479:
4480:```typescript
4481:new WorldHistoryRecorder<TEventMap, TCommandMap, TDebug>(config: {
4482:  world: World<TEventMap, TCommandMap>;
4483:  capacity?: number;
4484:  commandCapacity?: number;
4485:  debug?: { capture(): TDebug | null };
4486:  captureInitialSnapshot?: boolean;
4487:})
4488:```
4489:
4490:### Methods
4491:
4492:#### `connect()`
4493:
4494:```typescript
4495:connect(): void
4496:```
4497:
4498:Starts recording world diffs and command outcomes. Optionally stores an initial snapshot.
4499:Starts recording world diffs, command submission outcomes, command execution outcomes, and tick failures. Optionally stores an initial snapshot.
4500:
4501:#### `disconnect()`
4502:
4503:```typescript
4504:disconnect(): void
4505:```
4506:
4507:Stops recording.
4508:
4509:#### `clear()`
4510:
4511:```typescript
4512:clear(): void
4513:```
4514:
4515:Clears recorded history and refreshes the initial snapshot if `captureInitialSnapshot` is enabled.
4516:
4517:#### `getTickHistory()`
4518:
4519:```typescript
4520:getTickHistory(): Array<WorldHistoryTick<TEventMap, TDebug>>
4521:```
4522:
4523:Returns cloned recent tick entries.
4524:
4525:#### `getCommandHistory()`
4526:
4527:```typescript
4528:getCommandHistory(): Array<CommandSubmissionResult<keyof TCommandMap>>
4529:```
4530:
4531:Returns cloned recent command outcomes.
4532:
4533:#### `getCommandExecutionHistory()`
4534:
4535:```typescript
4536:getCommandExecutionHistory(): Array<CommandExecutionResult<keyof TCommandMap>>
4537:```
4538:
4539:Returns cloned recent command execution outcomes.
4540:
4541:#### `getTickFailureHistory()`
4542:
4543:```typescript
4544:getTickFailureHistory(): TickFailure[]
4545:```
4546:
4547:Returns cloned recent tick failures.
4548:
4549:#### `findTick(tick)`
4550:
4551:```typescript
4552:findTick(tick: number): WorldHistoryTick<TEventMap, TDebug> | null
4553:```
4554:
4555:Returns one recorded tick entry or `null`.
4556:
4557:#### `getState()`
4558:
4559:```typescript
4560:getState(): WorldHistoryState<TEventMap, TCommandMap, TDebug>
4561:```
4562:
4563:Returns the full recorder state: initial snapshot, recent ticks, recent command submission outcomes, recent command execution outcomes, and recent tick failures.
4564:The returned `WorldHistoryState` includes `schemaVersion`.
4565:
4566:#### `summarizeWorldHistoryRange(state, options?)`
4567:
4568:```typescript
4569:summarizeWorldHistoryRange<TEventMap, TCommandMap>(
4570:  state: WorldHistoryState<TEventMap, TCommandMap, WorldDebugSnapshot>,
4571:  options?: { startTick?: number; endTick?: number },
4572:): WorldHistoryRangeSummary | null
