4638:### Probe Helpers
4639:
4640:```typescript
4641:createOccupancyDebugProbe(key: string, occupancy: OccupancyGrid): DebugProbe
4642:createVisibilityDebugProbe(key: string, visibility: VisibilityMap): DebugProbe
4643:createPathQueueDebugProbe(
4644:  key: string,
