208:- `docs/design/2026-04-27-synthetic-playtest-harness-design.md` (v10) for the full spec.
209:- `docs/design/ai-first-dev-roadmap.md` for how Spec 3 fits into the broader roadmap.
210:- `docs/guides/session-recording.md` for the underlying SessionRecorder/SessionReplayer machinery.
